codex
The independent checks agree on the key safeguard: a close estimate appears only in a rich-covariate 1-NN design, so I’m treating recovery as specification-dependent. I’m incorporating the estimator audit’s HC3 sandwich intervals (not a nearest-neighbor bootstrap) before running the final pipeline.
