Key result: the experimental benchmark is **$1,794**. The naive NSW-treated/CPS-control contrast is **−$8,498**. Matching gets close only for rich-covariate 1-NN specifications ($1,712 untrimmed; $2,088 trimmed); demographics-only and score-stratification specifications are substantially lower. The memo therefore adjudicates recovery as **only under favorable specifications**, not robustly.
